comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T19:03:39.106Z",codex-monica-api,Created after complete all-status tracker search and stable source-route comparison. pm-cli issue 635 records why the generic Plan creation workaround was required.
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T19:03:39.106Z",codex-monica-api,Never run mutating live Monica API operations; readOnlyMode stays true for all actual CLI validation.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T19:03:39.106Z",codex-monica-api,Systemic probe failure must be modeled separately from resource-level unsupported behavior.
