plan_validation[5]{text,command,expected}:
  Exact all-source coverage and production release gate passed.,"bun run verify:release:gates",830 tests and 100/100/100/100 coverage; 273 help checks; typecheck lint JSDoc LOC duplication build smoke workflow and history gates pass.
  Actual installed CLI remained read-only against the configured private instance.,"MONICA_E2E_TIMEOUT_MS=3000 MONICA_E2E_REQUEST_TIMEOUT_MS=1000 bun run test:e2e:readonly","95 total, 42 pass, 53 expected unavailable, 0 fail, mutation guards pass, settings restored."
  Dependency audit is clean after fixed transitive overrides.,bun audit,No vulnerabilities found.
  PR round-one CI findings fixed locally.,"bun run lint:source-quality && bun run typecheck && bun run test:coverage && bun audit",Portable Node-only quality discovery; 838 tests at exact coverage; zero vulnerabilities.
  Built artifact help audit is clean-runner portable.,"bun run build && bun run test:e2e:help",273/273 command help checks execute dist/index.js without a global link.
plan_decisions[1]{ts,author,decision,rationale,evidence}:
  "2026-07-21T19:03:55.583Z",codex-monica-api,Use Monica stable 4.x source routes as the authoritative parity baseline while retaining documented legacy variants as compatibility fallbacks.,Self-hosted versions drift; source-first primary routes plus narrow 404/405 fallbacks maximize correctness without masking server failures.,monicahq/monica routes/api.php at 32028ce and official monicahq.com/api docs
plan_discoveries[2]{ts,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T19:03:54.564Z",codex-monica-api,"Stable 4.x routes add statistics places lifeevents reminders/upcoming me/contact and use contacts/{contact}/work food introduction plus PUT avatar; live 500 is systemic Laravel logging/proxy failure."
  "2026-07-21T20:03:50.729Z",codex-monica-api,"Verified Monica stable 4.x source at commit 32028ce3ce79cef38df5d27a297e5b20680f0065, including routes/api.php and controller validation for statistics, account me/contact, places, life events, reminders/upcoming, contact introduction, avatar, work and food endpoints. Live read-only probing against the configured private instance exposed a server-side Laravel log permission failure returning HTTP 500; CLI capability reporting now classifies this as unavailable with support unknown rather than unsupported. No production Monica records were mutated."
